Text:
Here is a much more complete discography of Pat The Bunny (lead singer of Johnny Hobo). It includes all Johnny Hobo, some of which is not here, and everything by Wingnut Dishwashers Union (his other band).

http://www.kickasstorrents.com/johnny-hobo-wingnut-discography-t4105977.html
The torrent I linked to last comment is dead, and there are no seeds. I found a new source, however to Pat The Bunny's music, and I used it to create a much, MUCH improved torrent..
